 contacts within the watchmaking industry guillaume developed a modern and affordable version of his vintage chronograph no pretending here the brand does not hide its chinese production each piece is conceived in paris and manufactured in shenzhen enabling william l  to compete in this price range to initiate his project guillaume naturally chose the crowdfunding option and rapidly got very positive feedbacks and more importantly a community that shares its philosophy and gathered around him thanks to you it is now together that we continue to build william l  history william l  william l  william l  vintage chronograph gold black alligator wlorbcorcn regular price  special price  man add to wishlist more william l  william l  bicolore vintage chronograph brown buffalo leather wlacbcorbm regular price  special price  man add to wishlist more william l  william l  vintage calendar gold black brown wlojnrojcm regular price  special price  man add to wishlist more william l  william l  vintage calendar gold black wlojnrojcn regular price  special price  man add to wishlist more william l  william l  vintage calendar rose gold black alligator wlorbcorcn regular price  special price  man add to wishlist more william l  william l  small chronograph gold black brown croco wlojnrojcm regular price  special price  unisex add to wishlist more william l  william l  small chronograph rose gold brown silver wlorgocm regular price  special price  unisex add to wishlist more william l  william l  small chronograph brown silver wlacgocm regular price  special price  unisex add to wishlist more william l  william l  small chronograph black black wlacnrcn regular price  special price  unisex add to wishlist more william l  william l  small chronograph silver black wlorgocn regular price  special price  unisex add to wishlist more terms and conditions contact us about us sitemap secure payment express delivery newsletter subscribe subscribe and get  discount us ar bh be ca co dk fi f